name: Fantasy Farmland
description:
Welcome to Fantasy Farm Land

You have run out of food and need to find food and resources in order to survive. Go and start a new adventure and travel to the next village over. Have fun and explore all the different ways of farming and collecting different vegetables. From pumpkins to lettuce to carrots gather as many resources to grow your village.  Grow your land from starting with a small shed to a big house. Adventure deep into the whimsical forest.  What will you find?

This level is a small layout that gives you a visual view of what Fantasy Village looks like. Nothing in this current state of the level is grabbable yet. To be continued...
